   The County of San Bernardino strives to provide the highest level of
   public service to over 1.7 million residents while responsibly
   safeguarding the peoples economic and natural resources. The county is
   equally dedicated to constantly heightening the publics faith in
   government.
   The 18,000 professionals employed by the County of San Bernardino carry
   out their mission of public service through a variety of tasks all
   aimed at continually improving an excellent quality of life. This site
   serves as guide to those services as well as other aspects of county
   government and life here in San Bernardino County.
